  "stem": "<p><i>y</i> = <i>x</i>&sup2; &minus; 4</p><p><i>y</i> = &minus;<i>x</i> &minus; 2</p><p>If (<i>x</i>&#8321;, <i>y</i>&#8321;) and (<i>x</i>&#8322;, <i>y</i>&#8322;) are the two solutions to the system of equations above, what is the value of <i>x</i>&#8321; + <i>x</i>&#8322;?</p>",
