  "rationale": "<p>Choice B is correct. Setting <i>x</i>&sup2; &minus; 4 = &minus;<i>x</i> &minus; 2 gives <i>x</i>&sup2; + <i>x</i> &minus; 2 = 0. Factoring: (<i>x</i> + 2)(<i>x</i> &minus; 1) = 0, so <i>x</i>&#8321; = &minus;2 and <i>x</i>&#8322; = 1. The sum is &minus;1. Alternatively, by Vieta's, the sum of roots equals &minus;<i>b</i>/<i>a</i> = &minus;1.</p>",
